Oh No, It’s Raya Again
by De Fam (English Translation)

Oh no, oh no, oh no!
A month before Raya, just realized fasting starts tomorrow
Forgot to make intention, quick—Google it
Time flies so fast
Suddenly it’s the 24th night
Too late to buy flight tickets
Too late to rent a car
Oh no, oh no, oh no!

Oh no, it’s Raya again
My cookies didn’t turn out right
Rushing to weave ketupat
Rendang’s burnt in the pan
Oh no, it’s Raya again
Forgot to buy Raya clothes
Stuck in traffic on the way home
Looking right, looking left—
Still stuck!

Eh, eh, walking with a little swag
Trying to cook grandma’s rendang
Mama’s busy, the clothes aren’t even ironed—oh no!
Cookies got burnt, no one watched the oven
Dad’s samping (Raya sarong) is already missing
Oh no, oh no, oh no!

Oh no, it’s Raya again
My cookies didn’t turn out right
Rushing to weave ketupat
Rendang’s burnt in the pan
Oh no, it’s Raya again
Forgot to buy Raya clothes
Stuck in traffic on the way home
Looking right, looking left—
Still stuck!

In the evening, everyone’s happy
But I’m the only one alone
Trying to check Instagram Stories
But the WiFi’s so slo—(ugh!)
When Raya finally comes...

Oh no, it’s Raya again
My cookies didn’t turn out right
Rushing to weave ketupat
Rendang’s burnt in the pan
Oh no, it’s Raya again
Forgot to buy Raya clothes
Stuck in traffic on the way home
Looking right, oh, looking left—
Still stuck!
